&lt;p&gt;The Neurosciences Directorate is looking for a Receptionist/Clinic Prep Assistant to join our team in providing excellent and professional administrative and clerical support to the Neurosciences outpatient department located in the John Radcliffe Hospital. Hours of work will be Monday - Friday, will vary on a rotational basis and will be within the hours of 08:00 - 17:00.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will provide receptionist support for our busy outpatient department as well as ensuring that all health records are available and prepared for all Neuroscience outpatient clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a self-motivated and enthusiastic individual who is a good team player with a flexible approach to work. The Neurosciences directorate is an interesting and varied directorate with many opportunities for development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
